p.cl:
With these witnesses: Roger the prior of Furness; Ivo the dean of Copeland; Adam
                  the parson of Millum; Robert the priest of 'Punzurebi';
                  William of Esbie; John son of Pontius and William his son;
                  Edward son of Ulf and Ketill his brother; Richard son of
                  Pontius; Hugh son of Edward; Alan son of Ketill; WIlliam
                  Lubright.
